    <item>
      <title>台湾维持利率不变，经济为大选做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/taiwan-holds-rate-unchanged-as-economy-gears-up-for-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾央行在 2023 年最后一次会议上维持利率不变，在台湾为 1 月份关键选举做准备之际，借贷成本处于八年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/taiwan-holds-rate-unchanged-as-economy-gears-up-for-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 08:29:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典房地产、矿业股引领欧洲美联储后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/swedish-real-estate-wind-stocks-top-post-fed-rally-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储转向扭转大幅加息的方向后，瑞典房地产股票和矿业公司等欧洲股市遭受重挫，股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/swedish-real-estate-wind-stocks-top-post-fed-rally-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 08:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鸽派转向后交易员加大全球降息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/traders-boost-ecb-and-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-fed-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球市场适应美联储转向宽松政策，交易员在周四晚些时候欧洲央行和英格兰银行做出政策决定之前加大了对全球降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/traders-boost-ecb-and-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-fed-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 07:40:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行家躲避欧洲迄今为止最严格的 ESG 法律的全面影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/banks-win-reprieve-from-landmark-eu-law-on-due-diligence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟达成妥协以帮助该法案顺利通过，金融业将免受欧盟迄今为止最重要的 ESG 立法的全部影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/banks-win-reprieve-from-landmark-eu-law-on-due-diligence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 07:02:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本将利用更多税收激励措施鼓励工资上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/japan-to-use-more-tax-incentives-to-encourage-wage-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本自民党及其联盟伙伴公明党同意向大幅提高工资的公司提供更多税收优惠，这可能有助于提高日本实现央行削减刺激措施所需的工资增长和通胀良性循环的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/japan-to-use-more-tax-incentives-to-encourage-wage-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 06:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行降息推迟取决于新的预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/ecb-rate-cut-pushback-to-hinge-on-new-forecasts-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在借贷成本上升一年多之后，现在所有人的目光都集中在欧洲央行如何强力抵制降息押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/ecb-rate-cut-pushback-to-hinge-on-new-forecasts-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注美联储转向，美元跌至八月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/dollar-drops-to-weakest-since-august-as-fed-weighs-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元周四跌至四个月低点，因为交易员消化了迄今为止最明确的信号，即美联储激进的加息行动已经结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/dollar-drops-to-weakest-since-august-as-fed-weighs-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 01:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员押注降息，股票和债券上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储暗示明年降息后，股市和债券上涨，在通胀压力缓解的乐观情绪中释放了整个市场的看涨脉搏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
